17	//
18	// Loads file over the serial port into memory on the FPGA board.  This
19	// communicates with the first stage bootloader in software/bootloader.
20	// It expects the memory file to be in the format used by the Verilog
21	// system task $readmemh: each line is a 32 bit hexadecimal value.
22	// This may optionally also take a binary ramdisk image to load at 0x4000000.
23	//
24	
